movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: A GREAT MOVIE!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
review: I wasn't alive when the first second and third came out. But i know I'm Nine! but... i have all the star wars stuff! It was a Great Movie! if it was in the olypics! i would give it a ten! I loved everything! The droids, the gungans, the toydarains, the hutts, the... the... everything! It was a great movie! if you haven't seen it yet... well i have one thing to say. go see the movie!
